show.description:
In the ruthless tides of the corporate world, success is never an accident.
This is the story of a self-made man who, armed with vision, resilience, and relentless ambition, rises from humble beginnings to become the leader of a global empire.
Amid a battlefield of wealth, power, and betrayal, he must navigate not only fierce competitors but also the shadows within his own heart. Every decision he makes is a gamble — one that could either build an empire or tear it all down.
